image_analysis.description: A photograph taken from a doorway looking into a small utility or storage room. The room has beige walls, white crown molding, and a dark striped carpet. A ceiling light with a gold-colored base is on. There is an open ceiling tile revealing wires. On the left wall, there is a gray rectangular panel. A white plastic shopping bag with the word 'DUANE' visible is on the floor. In the background, there is a counter with various items including yellow power tools (possibly DeWalt or Ryobi), boxes, and a roll of paper towels. A black tool bag and other items are on the floor in the corner.
image_analysis.layout: Interior photograph showing a room through an open white door.

document_metadata.subject: Interior of a storage or utility room with tools and supplies

notes: The text 'DUANE' and 're' appear to be part of a 'Duane Reade' shopping bag logo. The number EFTA00000813 is a bates-style tracking number for the document collection.
